TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {31061=Copyright © 2015, 18308=In 1963, 18331=Tuesday, Jan. 15 — Effective with the next telephone directory due in March, all telephone numbers in Las Vegas will be changed to seven numerals, I.G. Eubanks, manager for Mountain States Telephone, announced.
